**Luna Node**

&lt;a href="https://lunanode.com/" target="_blank"&gt;Luna Node&lt;/a&gt; provides high quality unmanaged VPS hosting at an affordable price. We exclusively use KVM on all plans for the greater control that it gives users. At the moment we're offering various plans in Chicago with 512 MB to 8192 MB memory.

Budget plans come with RAID10 HDD storage and 5 IPv4 addresses (or, get 13 IPv4 addresses for $3.50/mo over standard prices). SSD KVM plans come with a single IPv4 address and RAID0 SSD storage.

On Budget VPS, we offer a custom VM control panel that features the typical management options (although we're currently still using SolusVM for our SSD KVM plans). Servers are provisioned out of SingleHop's Chicago datacenter.

